name: Corsair Vengeance 32GB DDR5
image_prompt: Corsair Vengeance DDR5 RAM kit, two black memory modules with aluminum heatspreaders, RGB lighting strip on top
description: High-performance DDR5 memory kit (2x16GB) running at 5600MHz with tight CL36 timings. Features aluminum heatspreader and Intel XMP 3.0 support for easy overclocking.

reviews.review_text: XMP profile worked first try. Solid 5600MHz performance.
Big upgrade from DDR4. Compiles are noticeably faster.
Good kit but RGB software is bloated.
